@startuml state
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam stateBackgroundColor #F0EEF8
skinparam stateBorderColor #3D108A
skinparam stateArrowColor #2E2E38
skinparam stateFontSize 13
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #E8F8F8
skinparam noteBorderColor #27ACAA
skinparam noteFontSize 12

[*] --> Unanswered : indicator loaded

Unanswered --> Answered : setAnswer(score 1 to 5)
Answered --> Answered : setAnswer(new score)

Answered --> EvidenceCapped : getEffectiveScore()\n[score >= 3, no evidence]
EvidenceCapped --> Answered : setEvidence(text)

Unanswered --> Skipped : skipIndicator()\n[not BCT; skips < 20% limit]
Answered --> Skipped : skipIndicator()\n[not BCT; skips < 20% limit]
Skipped --> Unanswered : unskipIndicator()

note right of EvidenceCapped
  Effective score forced
  to 2 in aggregation.
  Provide evidence to
  restore the true score.
end note

note right of Skipped
  score set to null,
  excluded from denominators.
  BCT indicators cannot
  be skipped.
end note

@enduml
